DEVOPS TOOLS 

i) maven
In java we cannot deploy project directly on server instead jar file is deoloyed 
In intellij,maven clean , after click install it will generate jar file in target folder .

ii) Sonarqube -->
-used for reviewing the code and find the bugs 
-automate process for reviewing

iii) Jfrog and nexus --> maintain the versions of project like project versions / java versions / jar files

iv) Terraform --> automates creation of ec2 /server

v) Grafanana and prometheous : used for monitoring of hardware 

vi) ELK (Elastic search , Logstash , Kibana)  used for monitoring of software logs

vii) Kubernetes :- helps to manage docker images

viii) docker


